      "block_type": "paragraph",
      "heading": "Offer is greater than $7,500,000",
      "heading_path": [
        "Special considerations",
        "One responsive offer",
        "Offer is greater than $7,500,000"
      ],
      "text": "You must contact a cost analyst to determine if further analysis is warranted as specified by the mandatory conditions set out in the Directive on the Use of Cost and Price Analysis Services (accessible only on the Government of Canada network).",
      "order": 5,
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "block_0006",
      "block_type": "paragraph",
      "heading": "Offer is greater than $7,500,000",
      "heading_path": [
        "Special considerations",
        "One responsive offer",
        "Offer is greater than $7,500,000"
      ],
      "text": "Once you have determined the offer represents fair value to Canada, the contract may be awarded using competitive authorities to the single responsive offeror. If you are not satisfied the offer represents fair value, you may consider negotiating with the offeror or cancelling and reissuing the solicitation.",
      "order": 6,
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "block_id": "block_0007",
      "block_type": "heading",
      "heading": "Offer is less than or equal to $7,500,000",
