      "text": "Once you have determined the offer provides fair value to Canada, the contract may be awarded using competitive authorities. If you are not satisfied that the offer represents fair value, you may consider negotiating or cancelling and reissuing the solicitation.",
      "order": 9,
      "metadata": {}
