      ],
      "text": "When the offer is from an offeror in a North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO) allied country (or a significant portion is being proposed to be subcontracted to an offeror in a NATO -allied country), you should consider using the services of the foreign offeror’s country’s government to conduct an assessment of the fairness and reasonableness of the offer.",
