      "block_type": "paragraph",
      "heading": "Evaluate joint venture offers",
      "heading_path": [
        "Special considerations",
        "Evaluate joint venture offers"
      ],
      "text": "The evaluation of such offers includes verifying that all members of the joint venture are identified and will be individually liable for the performance of the contract. If a financial capability assessment is done, then all members of the joint venture will be assessed.",
